    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK525">
<l>koṭuttalu miṉcolu māṟṟi ṉaṭukkiya</l>
<l>cuṟṟattāṟ cuṟṟap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will be surrounded by numerous relatives who manifests generosity and affability.</l>
            </lg>
